The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, taxi
1. the person who's sport is handball is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Birthday        | november | may | april |
| Pet         | dog       | pony    | rat       |
| Sport       | handball  | surfing | golf      |
| Transport   | taxi      | boat    | quad-bike |

