4. the person who likes turquise is the japanese##1
5. the turkish is on the far right##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
7. the indian is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Food          | peas     | pear   | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | epic   | drama      |
| Nationality   | japanese | indian | turkish    |
| Color     | turquise  | apricot   | chestnut |

